    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove requirements to undertake new training when renewing an SIA licence",
        "additional_details": "Having to undertake additional training when renewing an SIA licence costs time and money.",
        "background": "Security workers renewing their SIA licence are sometimes required to take additional training, when new topics have been added to SIA training requirements. These requirements should be removed, due to increased living costs and uncertain job prospects.",
